The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning and decision-making processes, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
